data.description: Welcome to 1091 Washington Drive! Built in 2001 and situated on a 1/4 acre lot, this home has 1,379 square feet to enjoy, plus an attached garage. 3 bedrooms downstairs and a bonus room over the garage, 2 full bathrooms, and a sun-filled eat-in kitchen that looks over the huge backyard! Fresh paint throughout, new LVP throughout, HVAC just serviced - you don't want to miss all the upgrades and charm this home has without an HOA in Grassfield/ Great Bridge school zones!
